{"tid":2068301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣係時候攪攪每年慣例嘅71遊行","createTime":"2020-06-17T14:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T14:59:02.000Z","uid":129068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"37eb4deb567bd76f97192baeeb383a1fead02255","tid":2068301,"uid":129068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:50:16.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"954a7a6af5166c5ebf350529595a9c924959c8ed","tid":2068301,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:50:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"45a95d3f7c880d2cf498fc83e6665a586064f00e","tid":2068301,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"仲加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428c3bfeea36c019b749013b98ad55ead71ee7c2","tid":2068301,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:54:05.000Z","msg":"之前話六月搞遊行 要求張健宗批准<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而架潛埋水<br />\n民陣已完成歷史任務"},{"pid":"e2332a61de8496f80bfec983371e9e91d9a1738b","tid":2068301,"uid":341865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:58:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人建國<br />\n香港獨立</span>"},{"pid":"48ea343c380cfea0900ae9e77a606ee6eedb628e","tid":2068301,"uid":55080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"送頭不了"}]}